Henrietta's timeless style developed by accidentally dipping her paintbrush into her coffee. It combines tradition with less hazardous digital methods, all of which has resulted in an inspiring, mutable and memorable body of work.";s:10:"post_title";s:16:"Henrietta Harris";s:12:"post_excerpt";s:0:"";s:11:"post_status";s:7:"publish";s:14:"comment_status";s:6:"closed";s:11:"ping_status";s:6:"closed";s:13:"post_password";s:0:"";s:9:"post_name";s:16:"henrietta-harris";s:7:"to_ping";s:0:"";s:6:"pinged";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2014-07-02 22:18:21";s:17:"post_modified_gmt";s:19:"2014-07-02 22:18:21";s:21:"post_content_filtered";s:0:"";s:11:"post_parent";s:1:"0";s:4:"guid";s:80:"http://stage.gladeye.org/internationalrescue/online/?post_type=artist&#038;p=173";s:10:"menu_order";s:1:"0";s:9:"post_type";s:6:"artist";s:14:"post_mime_type";s:0:"";s:13:"comment_count";s:1:"0";s:13:"discipline_id";s:1:"3";s:15:"discipline_name";s:12:"Illustration";s:15:"discipline_slug";s:12:"illustration";}i:15;O:8:"stdClass":26:{s:2:"ID";s:3:"174";s:11:"post_author";s:1:"1";s:9:"post_date";s:19:"2014-03-30 21:18:56";s:13:"post_date_gmt";s:19:"2014-03-30 21:18:56";s:12:"post_content";s:681:"Ingrid Cole is a highly established and recognised English illustrator who recently immigrated to New Zealand. Her impressive and distinct style has brought her major commissions from advertising agencies, record companies and a wide range of publications. Ingrid is excited by contrasts and aesthetic contradictions. Her use of colours are one of the most striking elements of her work and never fail to impress.

